com.tokelon.toktales.core.game.model

Interface IRectangle2f

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IRectangle2f.IMutableRectangle2f
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rectangle2fImpl

    public interface IRectangle2f
    A float precision rectangle in 2D space.

    Assumes positive Y-Axis goes DOWN and values include 0f.
    That means it's origin lies in the top left corner.

    Example:
        top=0f
    left=0f       right=64f
        bottom=32f

    Width = 64f
    Height = 32f
    Rectangle does contain (0f, 0f)
    Rectangle does not contain (0f, 32f) or (64f, 0f)
